  "descriptions": {
    "en": {
      "language": "en",
      "value": "military commander from the Sengoku period to the Azuchi-Momoyama period. Nada Kanki's second son. Lord of Musashi-Imaichi Castle and commander of Myokendake Castle. A vassal of the Otomo clan. Owari no kami, Omi no kami, Daisuke Minbu"
    },
    "ja": {
      "language": "ja",
      "value": "戦国時代から安土桃山時代の武将。奈多鑑基の次子。武蔵今市城城主、妙見嶽城城督。大友氏の家臣。尾張守、近江守、民部大輔"
    },
    "nl": {
      "language": "nl",
      "value": "commandant"
    }
